        "line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "产品线B是45、32、33、12，然后C是87、54、99、85——这条波动比较大，你注意一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "B和C都画好了，C确实起伏很明显。还有两条产品线对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "D是78、88、22、4，Q3Q4掉得厉害；E是22、29、75、33。五条线齐了，最后加市场基准的柱子。",
      "elements_involved": [
